data.description: Great space for the price on a corner lot. 4 Bedrooms with all new paint, new carpet and a brand new roof plus there's over a 1/3 acre of land. Corner lot. There is an extra long utility room that's 20' long. Siding on fascia and eaves for low maintenance. Great location for a great home!
